<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>237</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yáo yáo qiān lǐ gé bù duàn wǒ men bǐ cǐ de xiàng wǎng
 xuān jiào de xīn lián qǐ lái rú ài yī yàng zhēn chéng
 yī shēng de shì yán shì yǒng\001bù pàn lí zhǔ de míng
 shēng shēng sǐ sǐ huàn nán yǔ gòng
 cāng hǎi héng liú yuè sè méng lóng
 wǒ men yào tà shàng lí míng de lù chéng
 yīn wèi tài yáng yào cóng dōng fāng shēng qǐ
 wǒ men yào yíng jiē xīn de fù xìng xīn de shēng téng.</lyrics>
<title>xuān jiào de xīn lián qǐ lái 迦南237</title>
</song>